{
  "stem": "14463.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The whole thing was religion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were Hasidim, mostly were Hasidim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also there are also some institutions which was a first in Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was an institution which helped specifically pregnant women-- ladies, which could not afford food or could not afford the children because they were very religious, that every year, had a child, right?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so the city was intensely religious, intensely closed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody knew one another.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, even today, you find people from Chrzanow telling you who you are, and who your parents were, and who your grandparents are.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They know you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a tremendous bond.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was a tremendous sweetness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it went through you, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You were breathing with it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I used to go to-- So you asked me about the festivals.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So first of all, I told you a little bit about-- what's the name-- about Friday night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then Saturday-- Saturday morning was something incredible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The whole city was going davening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They went to prayers, the whole city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was not a soul.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, 90% were very religious. 10% were not so religious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But everybody went to prayers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now then, in our home, there was a tradition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In our home there was a tradition that we all went to grandfather for kiddush.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The whole family went to we went to synagogue.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He always brought some very poor people home for lunch, always.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there again.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother used to tell me, you know, when the boys were singing, people stood downstairs.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because we were living on the first floor, listening, how they were singing the Shabbos prayers because they had such beautiful voices.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they loved it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They love the melodies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They loved the songs.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
